#data cleaning
ques_val_col=[]
for i in list(data.columns):
    for j in range(len(data)):
        if(data[i][j]=="?"):
            ques_val_col.append(i)
            break

for i in range(len(data)):
    if((data["body_style"][i]=="hatchback" or data["body_style"][i]=="convertible" or data["body_style"][i]=="hardtop")and data["num_doors"][i]==0):
        data['num_doors'][i]="two"
    elif((data["body_style"][i]=="sedan" or data["body_style"][i]=="wagon")and data["num_doors"][i]==0):
        data["num_doors"][i]="four"
